{{Infobox Berry |name = Belue |image = [[File:Belue.png]] |caption = This glossy and colorful Berry has a mouthwateringly delicious appearance. However, it is awfully sour. |growtime = 5h 30m 0s |harvest = 20 berries |replant = 10% |points = 1,100 |flavor = {{!}} 10 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 30 }} '''Belue''' is a type of [[Berries|Berry]] that can be planted in [[Farm]]. It can be obtained by surrounding a [[Nomel]] with at least 130, but no more than 160 points of sour and no more than 80 points of all other flavours. The [[Nomel]] will then have a chance to mutate into this berry.
